welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Eastlake, a charming city known for its beautiful landscapes and friendly community. We hope you enjoy your stay and take some time to explore all that our city has to offer."

terminals.description: The main terminal at Burke Lakefront Airport serves both commercial and private flights.
